Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.11,0:00:05.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,那部电影好着吗?  好看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧  我下欢再找好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.06,0:00:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们最近都没劝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,开始有小腹了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,去个健身房好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可是健身房很贵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,都胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,加山
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,星奈  你在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你住这吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我家在隔壁镇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.72,0:00:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,用跑的到这?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,十几公里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好猛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.16,0:00:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,习惯就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你太太?  对  她是小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你好!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.37,0:01:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我们公司的员工  加山
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,老公受你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.31,0:01:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我才愛他照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.01,0:01:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那我洗走了  好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好猛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.63,0:01:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他比你大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是五十岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然迷上马拉松
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.64,0:01:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你同公司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.64,0:01:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我们公司的设计师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.68,0:01:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,仲是後杆图比女性更纤细
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.28,0:01:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好意外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.99,0:01:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你也跟他一起跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我也可以加入
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,马拉松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,马拉松
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,开始跑马和松吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,明天要努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,难得放假耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到你真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,开始跑马拉松
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是该做就做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,马拉松也开姑流行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还有前辈在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,喝杯荼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,给我水就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,请用  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,老公  来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,要走了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我嫂跑靣去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你慢慢来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他好猛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可以持续吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想跑马拉松
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你行吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,出好多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你很习惯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,已经能跟上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,快超过我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你看  我变瘦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这样没有防备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不好哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以  我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以  我身上都是汗  好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我回栗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你们也累瘫啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,跑太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我就说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊  加山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,果然不能勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,良升心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我每天都忙着工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,能跟人一起吃饭真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你可是前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏你我才有今天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我才羨慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.91,0:10:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有溫暖的本庭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有结婚吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我老婆跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很寂莫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:11:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你们夫妻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好好相处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,难讲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很少理我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他的兴趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就是嘛  这是我的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要发泄压力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,喝太多了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我去躺一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:12:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你喝太多了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我老公在那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我老公
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,还在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,伸舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,别出声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,别出声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,很少做爱巴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你很湿喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:17:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以  好大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你睡死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿太太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我在干什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,都结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就算缺乏做爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也不能外遇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,脑中一直回想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,加山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好想诲添看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:22:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好想添哟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我在说哈啊  不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.94,0:22:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,慢走  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.96,0:22:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了  ﻿慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.55,0:22:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.24,0:23:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.16,0:23:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我是加山
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.23,0:23:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我东西忘在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.54,0:23:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,今天起公不在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我拿个东西就好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.61,0:23:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.93,0:24:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,喝个水就念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.03,0:24:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
